      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "Feel this could be a race in three. DREAM ILLUSION (1) is in good form, scoring two back here running on hard then finishing a close-up fourth. Might be looking for the mile now and looks hard to hold out. Can't knock the form of ONLY US (3) who has won both starts here for the new yard. Fresh-up won over 1200m in a hot form race and then over 1400m latest. Has won at the mile and draws better today. Looks a top chance to bring up the winning hat-trick. CANDLELIGHT SHERIF (2) was just behind DREAM ILLUSION last time and looks next best. Fitter and could be over the odds. ODIN OMEN (10) was well held fresh but strips fitter and extra trip a plus. ALMA MATER (6) raced on speed last time and gave a sight. Can do the same this time.",
